{"tid":2274149,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Nikon相機業務惡化 海外大裁員兩成","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:21:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93a4a7ee33d9bbfb10b41e38e21374aa7df474a1","tid":2274149,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，始創於1917年的日本相機大廠Nikon周四(5日)宣布，該公司主要業務相機的業績表現，因智能手機興起和疫情擴散而惡化，為應對營運問題，將在2022年3月前於日本以外地區，裁員超過2,000人，數量約佔海外員工20%。另外，Nikon的半導體設備等精密機械業務也陷入困境，預計該業務本財年(截至2021年3月)的虧損將達500億日圓(約37億港元)。<br />\n<br />\nNikon透露，該公司的主要相機業務正在惡化，公司需要將營運規模調整至與銷售規模相符合，預計公司將把海外員工人數，降至約2016財年(截至2017年3月)的六成水平。此外，該公司還將透過把在日本宮城縣的數碼相機機身製造，集中遷移至泰國，以及整合銷售公司來降低成本。公司預計一系列節流措施，將讓公司降低超過800億日圓(約59億港元)的成本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/int/bkn-20201106160035470-1106_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Fcontent%2Fint%2Fbkn-20201106160035470-1106_00842_001.html&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9jrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=ab1da882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/int/bkn-20201106160035470-1106_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c1975b7673006d40f523ece91ab4c4b353bbb89","tid":2274149,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a7d341b9fb6ae54d7a70572e62f5fc1a772be1","tid":2274149,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"今年奧運年本應係所有相機廠最搵錢既一年，而家。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eacadd4d4b88560373b9a9169cbefec61a34d1b","tid":2274149,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":